dct_alternative_sm: Gallaecia regnum : descripta a F. Fer Ojea ord. oraed. et postmodum multis in locis emendata et aucta.
dct_description_sm: Decorative cartouche with cherubims holding a coat of arms and musical scale bars in upper left of map. Includes an illustration of Neptune holding a shell around the map title.
This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636, 1637, and 1680.
From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
